nodes.text: Fossfog's was an establishment on Axxila. There was an underworld bounty feed in the wine cellar.

Fossfog's appeared in The Bounty Hunter Code: From the Files of Boba Fett which was released on October 15, 2013 and written by Daniel Wallace, Ryder Windham and Jason Fry. It only appeared as an illustration, and no additional information was provided about Fossfog's other than its location on Axxila.
